#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.true_divide.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.true\\_divide"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.truediv.truediv:1 of
msgid "Returns a true division of the inputs, element-wise."
msgstr "返回输入的逐元素除法结果。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.truediv.truediv:3 of
msgid ""
"Instead of the Python traditional 'floor division', this returns a true "
"division.  True division adjusts the output type to present the best "
"answer, regardless of input types."
msgstr ""
"与 Python 传统的“地板除法”不同，此函数返回真除法结果。真除法会根据输入"
"类型调整输出类型以呈现最佳答案。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.truediv.truediv of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.truediv.truediv:7 of
msgid "Dividend tensor."
msgstr "被除数张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.truediv.truediv:9 of
msgid "Divisor tensor."
msgstr "除数张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.truediv.truediv:11 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须可以广播到输入形状。如果没有提供"
"或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度必须"
"等于输出数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.truediv.truediv:16 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr ""
"值为 True 表示在该位置计算通用函数（ufunc），值为 False 表示保留输出中的"
"原始值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.truediv.truediv of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.truediv.truediv:21 of
msgid "**out** -- Result is scalar if both inputs are scalar, tensor otherwise."
msgstr "**out** -- 如果两个输入都是标量，则结果是标量；否则是张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.truediv.truediv of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.truediv.truediv:25 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.truediv.truediv:26 of
msgid ""
"The floor division operator ``//`` was added in Python 2.2 making ``//`` "
"and ``/`` equivalent operators.  The default floor division operation of "
"``/`` can be replaced by true division with ``from __future__ import "
"division``."
msgstr ""
"地板除法运算符 ``//`` 在 Python 2.2 中添加，使得 ``//`` 和 ``/`` 成为等价"
"运算符。默认的地板除法运算 ``/`` 可通过 ``from __future__ import division"
"`` 替换为真除法。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.truediv.truediv:31 of
msgid ""
"In Python 3.0, ``//`` is the floor division operator and ``/`` the true "
"division operator.  The ``true_divide(x1, x2)`` function is equivalent to"
" true division in Python."
msgstr ""
"在 Python 3.0 中，``//`` 是地板除法运算符，而 ``/`` 是真除法运算符。``"
"true_divide(x1, x2)`` 函数等价于 Python 中的真除法。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.truediv.truediv:36 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.truediv.truediv:43 of
msgid ""
"# for python 2 >>> (x/4).execute() array([0, 0, 0, 0, 1]) >>> "
"(x//4).execute() array([0, 0, 0, 0, 1])"
msgstr ""
"# 对于 python 2 >>> (x/4).execute() array([0, 0, 0, 0, 1]) >>> (x//4)."
"execute() array([0, 0, 0, 0, 1])"

